    <h1>WHAT'S STREAMING?</h1>
    <h3>Streaming is accessing TV, film, and music through various content platforms by playing video and audio through your broadband connection. The level of streaming you can perform depends on the data you have in your broadband package. If you have unlimited streaming, you can access and use any of these platforms and use them at any time. Click on the images for information, click again to close the popover.</h3>
