          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">NETFLIX</h5>
        </div>

        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <button type="button" class="btn popover-right2" data-toggle="popover" data-trigger="focus" title="Prime Video" data-content="Prime Video is a video streaming service that's included in your Amazon Prime membership. You can watch thousands of titles on Prime Video at no additional cost — including many award-winning movies and critically acclaimed original TV series. Prime Video membership is $8.99 a month. Prime Video is included in a Prime membership. The membership fee for Amazon Prime is $119 per year or $12.99 per month."> <img src="/img/amazon.png" class="card-img-top" alt="amazon"></button>
